'''-{zh-cn:玛丽娜·克莱尔·惠勒; zh-tw:瑪麗娜·克萊爾·惠勒; zh-hk:衛雯雅}-''' {{post-nominals|country=GBR|QC}}（{{lang-en|Marina Claire Wheeler}}；{{bd|1964年|8月18日| }}）是一名英國[[大律師|大律師]]、作家和[[專欄作家|專欄作家]]，其前夫為現任英國首相[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]。衛雯雅是[[律師學院|律師學院]]的成員，專長為[[公法|公法]]和[[人权|人权]]，並在2016年獲委任為[[御用大律師|御用大律師]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/law/2016/jan/22/women-qcs-justine-thornton-marina-wheeler-is-legal-profession-still-sexist|title=New QCs Justine Thornton and Marina Wheeler: Is the legal profession still sexist?|last=Williams|first=Zoe|date=2016-01-22|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2020-01-25|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215202046/https://www.theguardian.com/law/2016/jan/22/women-qcs-justine-thornton-marina-wheeler-is-legal-profession-still-sexist|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
衛雯雅父親為[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]記者{{tsl|en|Charles Wheeler (journalist)|查理斯·衛拿}}爵士，其母親是衛拿第二任妻子、[[印度裔英國人|印度裔]][[旁遮普人|旁遮普]][[锡克人|锡克人]]迪寶·星。她的祖先可追溯至現今[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]境內的[[萨戈达|萨戈达]]，[[印巴分治|印巴分治]]後移居[[印度|印度]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Murtaza Ali Shah |url=http://www.geo.tv/article-183472-London-Mayor-wife-wish-to-visit-amazing-Pakistan |title=London Mayor, wife wish to visit 'amazing' Pakistan | World |website=Geo.tv |date=2015-05-02 |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2015-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016222850/http://www.geo.tv/article-183472-London-Mayor-wife-wish-to-visit-amazing-Pakistan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/880168/london-mayor-wife-wish-to-visit-pakistan-soon/ |title=London mayor, wife wish to visit Pakistan soon – The Express Tribune |website=Tribune.com.pk |date=2015-05-03 |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626230103/https://tribune.com.pk/story/880168/london-mayor-wife-wish-to-visit-pakistan-soon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

衛雯雅就讀{{tsl|en|European School, Brussels I|布魯塞爾第一歐洲學校}}，期間與[[鲍里斯·约翰逊|鲍里斯·约翰逊]]成為朋友<ref>{{cite web|title=The Boris Johnson story|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/7376621.stm|date=2008-05-04|last=Wheeler|first=Brian|publisher=BBC|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2008-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506144031/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/7376621.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1980年代初入讀[[剑桥大学菲茨威廉学院|剑桥大学菲茨威廉学院]]，曾為學生雜誌《{{tsl|en|Cantab (magazine)|Cantab}}》擔任編輯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2246935/Sir-Charles-Wheeler.html|title=Sir Charles Wheeler|date=2008-07-24|publisher=Telegraph|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416134252/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/2246935/Sir-Charles-Wheeler.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=family>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/borisjohnson/1924866/London-mayor-elections-2008-Family-of-influence-behind-Boris-Johnson.html|title=Family of influence behind Boris Johnson|date=2008-05-03|publisher=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]]|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2011-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110123154101/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/borisjohnson/1924866/London-mayor-elections-2008-Family-of-influence-behind-Boris-Johnson.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=family/><ref>{{cite web|first=Amit|last=Roy|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1080511/jsp/7days/story_9254821.jsp|title=Boris gets on his bike|publisher=The Telegraph of Calcutta|date=2008-05-11|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908202228/https://www.telegraphindia.com/1080511/jsp/7days/story_9254821.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 律師生涯 ==
衛雯雅畢業後回到布魯塞爾工作四年，1987年獲{{tsl|en|Call to the Bar|授予律師資格}}，到[[伦敦|伦敦]]的皇冠辦公室律師事務所實習，專攻[[心理健康|心理健康]]和[[歧視|歧視]]議題。2004年1月，衛雯雅晉身初級御用大律師B委員會<ref name=1cor>{{Cite web |url=http://www.1cor.com/1144/?form_668.replyids=48 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2008-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506061256/http://www.1cor.com/1144/?form_668.replyids=48 |archive-date=2008-05-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，2009年加入{{tsl|en|Legal professions in England and Wales|英格蘭及威爾斯法律專家|大律師紀律審裁處}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1cor.com/668/records/48/Marina%20Wheeler%20PDF%20CV.pdf|format=PDF|title=Marina Wheeler|website=1cor.com|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193038/http://www.1cor.com/668/records/48/Marina%20Wheeler%20PDF%20CV.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2016年2月成為[[御用大律師|御用大律師]]<ref>{{cite web|title=''Guardian Legal Network''|url=https://inforrm.wordpress.com/2016/01/11/news-queens-counsel-appointments-media-lawyers-take-silk/|accessdate=2019-07-25|date=2016-01-11|website=Inforrm.wordpress.com|archive-date=2017-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170311013805/https://inforrm.wordpress.com/2016/01/11/news-queens-counsel-appointments-media-lawyers-take-silk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

衛雯雅曾在自己的法律著作提及：

{{quote|我自己和很多同事的經驗都發現，我們處理的大部分歧視案件都是毫無根據，有一名同事表示比例高達六成......很多不受規管的顧問透過製造歧視案件賺錢，他們通常都不著眼於申請人的最大利益<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.1cor.com/1158/?form_1155.replyids=19 |title=When some are more equal than others |access-date=2010-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707061158/http://www.1cor.com/1158/?form_1155.replyids=19 |archive-date=2011-07-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。}}

== 家庭 ==
衛雯雅的胞妹思蓮·衛拿是[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]發言人<ref>{{cite web|title=Press contacts – Spokesperson's Service|url=http://ec.europa.eu/dgs/communication/pdf/list_spp_en.pdf|accessdate=2019-07-25|date=|format=PDF|website=Ec.europa.eu|archive-date=2017-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115200810/http://ec.europa.eu/dgs/communication/pdf/list_spp_en.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

莊漢生和{{le|阿萊格拉·莫斯廷－歐文|Allegra Mostyn-Owen}}的婚姻被宣佈無效後的數個星期<ref name="marriagedateperIndy">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/marina-wheeler-profile-the-brains-behind-boris-johnson-a6871006.html|title=Marina Wheeler, profile: The brains behind Boris Johnson|quotation=The Mayor’s wife couldn’t be more different from her husband – but are they on the same side of the EU debate?|date=2016-02-13|author=Andy McSmith|newspaper=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|accessdate=2018-09-07|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731231832/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/marina-wheeler-profile-the-brains-behind-boris-johnson-a6871006.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在1993年5月8日與衛雯雅奉子成婚<ref>{{cite web |last1=Brazell |first1=Emma |title=Boris Johnson reaches financial settlement with estranged wife after two years |url=https://web.archive.org/save/https://metro.co.uk/2020/02/18/boris-johnson-reaches-financial-settlement-estranged-wife-two-years-12259518/ |website=Metro |accessdate=2020-04-29}}</ref>。二人一同到布魯塞爾工作，莊漢生則為《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》報導[[欧洲议会|欧洲议会]]情況。夫妻二人的長女在1993年6月12日出生<ref name="marriagedateperIndy" />，他們總共有四名子女：拉娜·萊蒂思、米羅·亞瑟、嘉西亞·碧翠絲和費義多·亞波羅<ref name="family" />。

莊漢生出軌的指控曝光後，夫妻二人在2018年9月宣布早前已經分居<ref name="EllBad">{{cite news |last=Osborne |first=Samuel |title=Boris Johnson announces divorce from barrister Marina Wheeler after 25 years of marriage |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-divorce-marina-wheeler-marriage-brexit-affairs-mp-qc-children-a8526806.html |accessdate=2018-09-07 |newspaper=[[獨立報|The Independent]] |date=2018-09-07 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042731/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/boris-johnson-divorce-marina-wheeler-marriage-brexit-affairs-mp-qc-children-a8526806.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並已開展離婚程序<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-politics-johnson-idUSKCN1LN10P|title=Former British Foreign Secretary Boris Johnson and wife to divorce|date=2018-09-07|website=Reuters.com|access-date=2019-06-28|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813090302/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-politics-johnson-idUSKCN1LN10P|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二人在2020年2月就財產安排達成協議<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news/pm-reaches-financial-settlement-with-estranged-wife-g8dxvg878 |title=PM reaches financial settlement with estranged wife |first=Jonathan |last=Ames |newspaper=The Times |publisher= |date=2020-02-18 |accessdate=2020-02-18 |archive-date=2020-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928150336/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news/pm-reaches-financial-settlement-with-estranged-wife-g8dxvg878 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年8月，衛雯雅證實年初確診[[子宮頸癌|子宮頸癌]]，已進行兩次手術<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/i-put-off-test-that-spotted-my-cervical-cancer-says-pm-s-wife-qdnzt7mm3|title=I put off test that spotted my cervical cancer, says Boris Johnson’s wife Marina Wheeler|publisher=The Times|date=2019-08-12|access-date=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305140758/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/i-put-off-test-that-spotted-my-cervical-cancer-says-pm-s-wife-qdnzt7mm3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

